Delhi Corona Daily Report: 24 May

#Delhi reported 508 new cases of Covid-19 in the last 24 hours while 273 patients recovered and 30 patients succumbed to the deadly virus in the same period.

Active cases in the capital stands at 6617.

#COVID19India #Covid_19india  #Covid_19 https://t.co/9Ltkw0aube
